jcsp.net

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • jcsp.net.Profile

  • public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object

    This class is used to hold profiles of Nodes and Links.

    Node profiles are not currently used.

    Profile functionality is still being implemented.
